The World's Strangest Superheroes are back and better than ever! The Doom Patrol has returned to DCUniverse (And HBOMax) and we couldn't be happier with this second season. The gang is all together but still reeling from their battle with Mr. Nobody, while mysterious villains prepare to come out of the woodwork to test Robotman, Negative Man, Elastigirl, Crazy Jane and Cyborg. When Niles Caulder's daughter Dorothy gets loose with the power to bring her imaginary friends to life, it becomes a race against time to save Dorothy and the rest of the world from pure unbridled destruction! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

